snippet.title: Mortal Kombat 1 – Official Takeda Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
He’s ready to add some trophies to his wall. Play him this weekend at #EVO2024!

Takeda and Ferra join MK1 on July 23. https://www.mortalkombat.com/purchase
It's In Our Blood. Discover a reborn Mortal Kombat Universe created by Fire God Liu Kang. Mortal Kombat 1 ushers in a New Era of the iconic franchise with a new fighting system, game modes, and Fatalities!
